<i>Previously on Smallville ...</i>

2
00:00:03,021 --> 00:00:04,230
Tell me what you've got

3
00:00:04,634 --> 00:00:09,137
Jor-El: I've warned you that the elements
could not fall into the hands of a human.

4
00:00:09,138 --> 00:00:11,589
The three must become one.

5
00:00:11,590 --> 00:00:12,906
No!

6
00:00:26,847 --> 00:00:31,608
In approximately 3 hours,
a meteor shower will hit Smallville.

7
00:00:31,609 --> 00:00:35,766
I want you to have this.
I somehow know that it's meant for you.

8
00:00:35,914 --> 00:00:40,016
Your curiousity always land you in
dangerous positions.

9
00:00:40,175 --> 00:00:43,830
Lex: Where is it?
- You just want the stone, don't you?

10
00:00:43,969 --> 00:00:45,969
I don't have the stone.

11
00:00:46,804 --> 00:00:50,981
Lex: Who did this? You know more than
you're telling me, Chloe.

12
00:00:51,089 --> 00:00:52,048
Who took the element?!

13
00:00:52,049 --> 00:00:54,800
Lana, you're talking like we're never
going to see each other again.

14
00:00:55,242 --> 00:00:56,742
I love you.

15
00:00:57,003 --> 00:00:58,450
I love you too.

16
00:01:27,528 --> 00:01:30,663
<i>And now, the Season Premiere of
Smallville.</i>

17
00:03:39,352 --> 00:03:42,352
Jor-El: Kal-El, you have travelled far.

18
00:03:43,221 --> 00:03:49,221
One journey has ended.
A new journey is about to begin.

19
00:03:54,216 --> 00:03:57,701
Welcome home, my son.

